        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3370787674" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer60290900380841909">4.5 stars....I’m better for having read. Intriguing and very well done. It only lagged in a few spots. Nothing wrong with continuing my education. More than likely sacrificed hitting my reading challenge goal but sometimes that’s ok. In this case, it’s ok. Who or what will I learn about next? </span>

          </span>
